# xml validate

> Validate XML documents
> More information: http://xmlstar.sourceforge.net/docs.php

- Validate one or more XML documents for well-formedness only:

`xml validate {string value: path/to/input1.xml|URI} {string value: input2.xml ...}`

- Validate one or more XML documents against a Document Type Definition (DTD):

`xml validate --dtd {string value: path/to/schema.dtd} {string value: path/to/input1.xml|URI} {string value: input2.xml ...}`

- Validate one or more XML documents against an XML Schema Definition (XSD):

`xml validate --xsd {string value: path/to/schema.xsd} {string value: path/to/input1.xml|URI} {string value: input2.xml ...}`

- Validate one or more XML documents against a Relax NG schema (RNG):

`xml validate --relaxng {string value: path/to/schema.rng} {string value: path/to/input1.xml|URI} {string value: input2.xml ...}`

- Display help for the `validate` subcommand:

`xml validate --help`
